    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/f13089a8239d421ea1ddb18cc31d5c15.poster.avif?t=1748915450\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/f13089a8239d421ea1ddb18cc31d5c15.webm?t=1748915450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/f13089a8239d421ea1ddb18cc31d5c15.mp4?t=1748915450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Slimenator》中，选择你的英雄（或至少是足够勇敢的人），与准备把你的冒险变成粘乎乎混乱的史莱姆大军对抗。在充满挑战的关卡中做出战略选择，适应新的危险和机会。每一次冒险都是独一无二的，充满惊喜和证明自己不仅仅是怪物的零食的机会。你准备好粉碎史莱姆，成为真正的冠军了吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可供选择的多个独特角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百种魔法技能、武器和配件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次开始新的冒险时，地图布局都会变化，每个转弯都带来新的挑战。在旅途中遇到不同的boss。每一次的挑战都不同，让每次游戏都成为一次新鲜而激动人心的体验！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图上的事件可能会帮助你或对你造成伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同类型的挑战（围攻、死亡竞赛、波次等）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有独特的技能树！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量史莱姆！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/5240e377da2d0773f1cb28dfa2ec0397.apng?t=1748915450\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/5240e377da2d0773f1cb28dfa2ec0397.poster.avif?t=1748915450\" class=\"bb_img\" width=66 height=18 /></picture></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/2954a87016bf7e6b3a8daa7162d8f7ac.poster.avif?t=1748915450\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/2954a87016bf7e6b3a8daa7162d8f7ac.webm?t=1748915450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331810/extras/2954a87016bf7e6b3a8daa7162d8f7ac.mp4?t=1748915450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
